                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d6"><locus target="#190v"/><desc><ref type="authFile" corresp ="AT1075PresentationJesus"/> Simon with <persName ref="PRS5684JesusCh"/> on his lap. <persName ref="PRS6819Mary"/> , holding a dove, looks on from upper right. She is attended by <persName ref="PRS5764Joseph"/> (left) and <persName ref="PRS8417Salome"/> (right). To the right and below three elders reach out and touch the garment of the seated figure</desc></decoNote>
